data.description: The gated entry leads to peaceful tranquility on this level 14 acres with approx. 10-12 acres in timber! Bring your creative ideas to make this home shine! Some of the work is already done for you - large, beautiful Trex deck and railing on the front, 2-year old furnace and heat pump, approx. 3 year old stainless dishwasher and refrigerator, 50-year presidential comp roof (installed in 1995), vinyl windows on the main floor (aluminum up). There's a perfect shop for all your projects that's approx. 20' X 40' with w/240 wiring and an air compressor and mostly concrete floor. There's also a generator plug by the sliding door on the exterior so you don't have to be concerned with not having power in the winter. Want a 2nd shop or a barn? There's also a large concrete pad (to accommodate a hardship manufacture home) near the house. The possibilities are endless with lots of room for livestock and farming!
